trans-unit.source: Testing the behavior of complex models has always bugged me. Sometimes models have many restrictions or many related objects which they depend on. One solution would be to use traditional fixtures dumped from your production database. But while in development when database schemes are changing frequently, it can be time consuming and sometimes difficult to deep track of changes and what each dump contains.
